Munin was started by Jimmy Olsen late 2003, based on RRD tool by Tobi Oetiker.
Development has slowed down since 2005, but Munin is a stable tool and is still
maintained.

Beispielhafte Installation
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-the-munin-monitoring-tool-on-ubuntu-14-04

Webserver notwendig. Plugins vom Webserver fuer Rendering Features.

Installationsguides nur fuer linux. windows wirkt hacky.
http://munin-monitoring.org/wiki/HowToMonitorWindows
https://github.com/munin-monitoring/munin-node-win32

